  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK909">
<l>aṟaviṉaiyu māṉṟa poruḷum piṟaviṉaiyum </l>
<l>peṇṇēval ceyvārka ṇil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>From those who obey the commands of their wives are to be expected neither deeds of virtue, nor those of wealth nor (even) those of pleasure.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
